    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331050/extras/cc99fefb3cc8c35244c933df87ea3691.avif?t=1746776644\" width=590 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「UC病！咖啡厅夫妻的愉快抗病生活」是由日本知名游戏社团神聖田中帝国制作，Hanabi games汉化发行的一款RPG游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331050/extras/8931370c3ae1f68b0ad92608ed95cb26.avif?t=1746776644\" width=550 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在和平的街道，有着一对经营着咖啡店的年轻夫妻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但在某天，丈夫奥伦突然被神秘的魔物袭击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幸运的是，人并没有受到严重伤害，但却有了其他的问题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那个魔物……携带着只有独角兽会携带的UC菌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被这种菌寄宿与大脑的奥伦换上了名为【UC病】的怪病。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了治好奥伦所患的这种怪病，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >则需要【独角兽的角】作为素材制作的药物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331050/extras/754257c3c1457328f17fea0bd682f0e6.avif?t=1746776644\" width=550 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331050/extras/afe79ce6b9e6dae2f9d57cfb42d3fffe.avif?t=1746776644\" width=550 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331050/extras/c09d0e028a31b321bff6f265e4af734b.avif?t=1746776644\" width=550 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=